---
description: Supabase SQL migrations (grants + RLS)
globs:
  - "supabase/migrations/**"
alwaysApply: false
---

Before adding or editing `supabase/migrations/`:

- Read `/ai_context/03_SECURITY_RULES.md` (Supabase section).
- Every new `public` table: `GRANT` to `service_role` in the same file as RLS; `REVOKE` from `anon` / `authenticated` when the table is backend-only.
- Grant `anon` / `authenticated` only when RLS policies intentionally expose rows via the Data API (e.g. token-scoped order reads).
